# Start/Stop/Reboot a VM


- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Manage your Vms" 
- At the right most side of the VM name you can see option to ' Start/Stop/Reboot ' the VM. 
- Click on the respective symbol to start,stop or reboot the VM
